FRC 6672 is proud to present our CAD for our 2024 robot Flex:

Flex1337×1037 90.8 KB

Flex OnShape CAD

This is the finished product of 6672’s 2024 season, and we are grateful for all the people who made this possible. Over the summer, I revised the CAD to better reflect the robot we had in real life, and hopefully, this will be helpful to anyone looking back at robot designs in the future. This robot was meant to be as simple as possible yet have the capability to do everything possible in the 2024 season.

Our intake took inspiration from 95’s Chief Delphi thread and our climb from the WCP Competitive Concept. And in between all of that, many Chief Delphi threads helped produce this robot.

The CAD file is separated into the different sub-assemblies of the robot and their up to date constructions. If you have any questions about the robot or some aspect of our design process, feel free to ask them or email us at fusioncorpsengineering2024@gmail.com
